<br>
<br>
<b>- To make Sale </b>Select Master -> Make New Sale
<br>
<br>
<img src="[% c.uri_for("/static/images/tutorial_2.jpg")%]" id="img3" />
<br><br>
- First Select product and then select one of the available stock
<br><br>
<img src="[% c.uri_for("/static/images/make_a_sale_1.jpg") %]"><br>
<br><br>
- Fill up the sale form 
<br>
<br>
<img src="[% c.uri_for("/static/images/make_a_sale_90.jpg") %]" id="img4"><br>
<br>
<br>
<b>- To take print out of sales invoice</b> Select Listing -> Sales Invoice
